menu "IOTMER example 05 (BLE Wi‑Fi + claim demo)"

    config IOTMER_05_DEMO_CLAIM_CODE
        string "Optional: demo claim code (lab, bind without GATT claim.set)"
        default ""
        help
            If set (e.g. pc_... from your backend), firmware uses it for bind-claim when no
            claim_code was received on the Claim GATT. Leave empty in production: use
            the …0404… characteristic or pc_ble_client --claim.

endmenu
